        <detaileddescription>
<para><blockquote><para><bold>TODO alumnos:</bold></para>
<para>✅ 1. Return the value of the field <computeroutput>flag_pressed</computeroutput>. Call the function <computeroutput><ref refid="stm32f4__button_8c_1ad71ae6d66617d620e1d83a18328e2044" kindref="member">_stm32f4_button_get()</ref></computeroutput> to get the button struct. <linebreak/>
</para>
</blockquote></para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
